Facete poeta deridet pauperes clientes, qui nummos defodiunt sive condunt in imo fundo loculorum vacuorum. De constructione „defossa in loculis” conferas Ovid.

Fast. II vs. 642: „sive lapis sive es defossus in agro stipes.'' VS. 54—55.
